create database platafroma;

use plataforma;


CREATE TABLE `alumnos` (
  `clave` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `nombre` varchar(40) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `app` varchar(40) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `apm` varchar(40) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `clave_carrera` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`clave`),
  KEY `Alumnos_Carrera_ibfk` (`clave_carrera`),
  CONSTRAINT `Alumnos_Carrera_ibfk` FOREIGN KEY (`clave_carrera`) REFERENCES `carrera` (`clave`) ON UPDATE CASCADE,
  CONSTRAINT `Alumnos_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`clave`) REFERENCES `usuario` (`clave`) ON UPDATE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE `carrera` (
  `clave` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `nombre` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`clave`)
);

CREATE TABLE `configuracion` (
  `ruta` varchar(150) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL
) ;

CREATE TABLE `cursos` (
  `clave` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `nombre` varchar(40) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `descripcion` mediumtext CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `foto` mediumblob NOT NULL,
  tema varchar(30) not null,
  `clave_carrera` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`clave`),
  KEY `Cursos_Carrera_pbfk` (`clave_carrera`),
  CONSTRAINT `Cursos_Carrera_pbfk` FOREIGN KEY (`clave_carrera`) REFERENCES `carrera` (`clave`) ON UPDATE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE `inscrito` (
  `clave_alumno` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `clave_curso` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `avance` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`clave_alumno`,`clave_curso`),
  KEY `Inscrito_Curso_pbfk` (`clave_curso`),
  CONSTRAINT `Inscrito_Alumno_pbfk` FOREIGN KEY (`clave_alumno`) REFERENCES `alumnos` (`clave`) ON UPDATE CASCADE,
  CONSTRAINT `Inscrito_Curso_pbfk` FOREIGN KEY (`clave_curso`) REFERENCES `cursos` (`clave`) ON UPDATE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE `lecciones` (
  `clave` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `nombre` varchar(60) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `secuencia` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `clave_curso` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`clave`),
  KEY `fk_Cursos_Lecciones` (`clave_curso`)
);

CREATE TABLE `preguntas` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `enunciado` varchar(200) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `imagen` mediumblob,
  `id_tema` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `Preguntas_Temas_pbfk` (`id_tema`)
);


CREATE TABLE `recursos` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `archivo` varchar(100) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `descripcion` varchar(100) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `id_tema` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `Recursos_Temas_pbfk` (`id_tema`)
);

CREATE TABLE `respuestas` (
  `idrespuesta` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `idpregunta` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `enunciado` varchar(100) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `imagen` mediumblob,
  PRIMARY KEY (`idrespuesta`),
  KEY `Respuestas_Preguntas_pbfk` (`idpregunta`)
);

CREATE TABLE `temas` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `nombre` varchar(40) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `secuencia` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `id_leccion` int(10) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `Lecciones_Temas_pbfk` (`id_leccion`)
);

CREATE TABLE `usuario` (
  `clave` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `password` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `tipo` char(2) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `activo` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  PRIMARY KEY (`clave`)
);
